      "description": "Tabulated elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus for Ti-6Al-4V ELI screw and rod stock, plus UHMWPE block material, sourced from coupon-level tensile testing conducted by the device manufacturer. These inputs were used to parameterize the bilinear isotropic hardening material model in the FEA ensemble. The material lot tested predates the minor geometry revision issued in model build v3r2; the engineering team assessed the revision as altering only rod-to-screw contact surface finish tolerances and concluded that bulk material constitutive properties remain unaffected, making re-characterization unnecessary.",
